room_title: Escape room "Vlad" by Conari Escape Rooms in Jefferson City
room_address: 514 E High St Jefferson City, MO 65101
room_description: October 13, 1564. It has been 300 years since the great Van Helsing discovered the existence of the antidote to the vampiric plague. Thought to be pure myth, the antidote was said to be locked away in Vlad Dracula’s castle. Van Helsing came close to finding Vlad’s hidden lair inside the evil fortress, but was unsuccessful. Now it is up to you to pick up where mr. Helsing left off and find the antidote to destroy Vlad and stop the vampiric plague from spreading!
